::KitKat::

She yelled again out the door of the base.  "Who is it that you are 
requesting that come out to you? There is only one female here and 
that's me.  So you had better figure out if your at the right base."

She turned and looked at Drillbit.  She leaned over and whispered 
into is ear,"Thank you for last night. It was wonderful."  She kissed 
him on the cheek and turned her head back out the crack in the door.

"So who do you want?" she yelled again.
